This is the entry point of the BackupSuite. 
From this point you can start all available options of the BackupSuite. 

Such as:
- Make a backup to HDD (and USB when conditions are met);
- Make a backup directly onto an USB-stick;;
- Make a backup to MMC;
- Restore a backup or flash a new image;
- Show the changelog of the last release(s);
- Open these help screens.
